title: Where are the Women in Crypto and NFTs?
itunes:title: Where are the Women in Crypto and NFTs?
description:
What the heck's an NFT? And how are women involved in this world? As cryptocurrency and NFTs continue to explode, we break down some definitions, some finance, some history and where women fit into this digital landscape.
